title: South Africa 20 Year bond Yield
description: South Africa 20 Year Bond Yield was 11.70 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Africa 20 Year bond Yield reached an all time high of 14.25 in March of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Africa 20Y.
